<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>GridStack Vanilla Demo</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f5f5f5;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .controls {
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .controls button {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin-right: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      border: none;
      background: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    .controls button:hover {
      background: #45a049;
    }

    .controls button.danger {
      background: #f44336;
    }

    .controls button.danger:hover {
      background: #da190b;
    }

    .grid-stack {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px;
      min-height: 400px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .grid-stack-item-content {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: move;
    }

    .widget-header {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      padding: 10px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .widget-close {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      border: none;
      color: white;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .widget-close:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    }

    .examples {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .example-section {
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .example-section h2 {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .example-section p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>🎯 GridStack Vanilla TypeScript Demo</h1>

    <div class="controls">
      <button id="addWidget">添加网格项</button>
      <button id="addRandom">添加随机网格项</button>
      <button id="compact">紧凑布局</button>
      <button id="toggleFloat">切换浮动模式</button>
      <button id="save">保存布局</button>
      <button id="load">加载布局</button>
      <button id="toggleStatic">切换静态模式</button>
      <button id="clearAll" class="danger">清空所有</button>
    </div>

    <div id="grid" class="grid-stack"></div>

    <div class="examples">
      <div class="example-section">
        <h2>📚 功能说明</h2>
        <p>
          这是一个基于 GridStack 的 Vanilla TypeScript 示例。支持以下功能：
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>✅ 拖拽移动网格项</li>
          <li>✅ 调整网格项大小</li>
          <li>✅ 动态添加/删除网格项</li>
          <li>✅ 保存和加载布局</li>
          <li>✅ 静态模式切换</li>
          <li>✅ 浮动布局</li>
          <li>✅ 紧凑布局</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script type="module" src="/src/main.ts"></script>
</body>
</html>
